SELECT "session_id" FROM "playback" AS "p" LEFT JOIN "ads" AS "a" ON "p"."customer_id"="a"."customer_id" AND "a"."timestamp" BETWEEN "p"."start_time" AND "p"."end_time" WHERE "ad_id" IS NULL

SELECT "SESSION_ID" FROM "PLAYBACK" WHERE "SESSION_ID" NOT IN (SELECT "SESSION_ID" FROM "PLAYBACK" AS "P" JOIN "ADS" AS "A" ON "A"."CUSTOMER_ID"="P"."CUSTOMER_ID" WHERE "TIMESTAMP" BETWEEN "START_TIME" AND "END_TIME")
SELECT "a"."session_id" FROM "playback" AS "a" LEFT JOIN "ads" AS "b" ON "a"."customer_id"="b"."customer_id" AND "timestamp" BETWEEN "start_time" AND "end_time" WHERE "b"."customer_id" IS NULL

SELECT "session_id" FROM "playback" AS "p" WHERE "p"."customer_id" NOT IN (SELECT "a"."customer_id" FROM "ads" AS "a" WHERE "a"."customer_id"="p"."customer_id" AND "a"."timestamp">="p"."start_time" AND "a"."timestamp"<="p"."end_time")
SELECT "session_id" FROM "playback" AS "p" WHERE "p"."customer_id" NOT IN (SELECT "a"."customer_id" FROM "ads" AS "a" WHERE "a"."timestamp">="p"."start_time" AND "a"."timestamp"<="p"."end_time")

SELECT DISTINCT "session_id" FROM "Playback" AS "p" WHERE "p"."customer_id" NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT "a"."customer_id" FROM "Ads" AS "a" WHERE "a"."timestamp"<="p"."end_time" AND "a"."timestamp">="p"."start_time")

SELECT "session_id" FROM "Playback" AS "p" LEFT JOIN "Ads" AS "a" ON "a"."customer_id"="p"."customer_id" AND "p"."start_time"<="a"."timestamp" AND "p"."end_time">="a"."timestamp" WHERE "a"."customer_id" IS NULL ORDER BY 1

SELECT "session_id" FROM "playback" WHERE "session_id" NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT ("p"."session_id") FROM "playback" AS "p" JOIN "ads" AS "a" ON "p"."customer_id"="a"."customer_id" WHERE "a"."timestamp" BETWEEN "p"."start_time" AND "p"."end_time")

SELECT "session_id" FROM "Playback" WHERE "session_id" NOT IN (SELECT "session_id" FROM "Playback" AS "drv" JOIN "Ads" AS "ad" ON "drv"."customer_id"="ad"."customer_id" AND "ad"."timestamp" BETWEEN "drv"."start_time" AND "drv"."end_time")

SELECT DISTINCT "p1"."session_id" FROM "Playback" AS "p1" LEFT JOIN "Ads" AS "a1" ON "a1"."customer_id"="p1"."customer_id" AND ("a1"."timestamp">="p1"."start_time" AND "a1"."timestamp"<="p1"."end_time") WHERE "a1"."ad_id" IS NULL

WITH "temp1" AS (SELECT "a".*,"b"."ad_id" FROM "Playback" AS "a" LEFT JOIN "Ads" AS "b" ON "a"."customer_id"="b"."customer_id" AND "b"."timestamp">="a"."start_time" AND "b"."timestamp"<="a"."end_time") SELECT DISTINCT "session_id" FROM "temp1" WHERE "ad_id" IS NULL
SELECT "session_id" FROM "playback" AS "p" LEFT JOIN "ads" AS "a" ON "p"."customer_id"="a"."customer_id" AND "a"."timestamp" BETWEEN "p"."start_time" AND "p"."end_time" WHERE "a"."timestamp" IS NULL

SELECT "session_id" FROM "Playback" WHERE "session_id" NOT IN (SELECT "session_id" FROM "Playback" AS "p" JOIN "Ads" AS "a" ON "a"."customer_id"="p"."customer_id" WHERE "start_time"<="timestamp" AND "end_time">="timestamp")
SELECT "p"."session_id" FROM "playback" AS "p" LEFT JOIN "ads" AS "a" ON "p"."customer_id"="a"."customer_id" AND ("timestamp" BETWEEN "start_time" AND "end_time") WHERE "a"."ad_id" IS NULL

WITH "customers_who_saw_ads" AS (SELECT "customer_id","timestamp" FROM "Ads") SELECT DISTINCT "p"."session_id" FROM "Playback" AS "p" LEFT JOIN "customers_who_saw_ads" AS "c" ON "c"."customer_id"="p"."customer_id" AND "c"."timestamp" BETWEEN "p"."start_time" AND "p"."end_time" WHERE "c"."customer_id" IS NULL

WITH "TMP" AS (SELECT DISTINCT "session_id" FROM "Playback" AS "p" JOIN "ads" AS "a" ON "p"."customer_id"="a"."customer_id" AND "timestamp"<="end_time" AND "timestamp">="start_time") SELECT DISTINCT "session_id" FROM "playback" AS "p" LEFT JOIN "ads" AS "a" ON "p"."customer_id"="a"."customer_id" WHERE "session_id" NOT IN (SELECT "session_id" FROM "tmp")

SELECT "B"."session_id" FROM (SELECT "A"."session_id",MAX("A"."label") AS "max_label" FROM (SELECT "p"."session_id",CASE WHEN "a"."timestamp"<"p"."start_time" OR "a"."timestamp">"p"."end_time" OR "a"."timestamp" IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS "label" FROM "Playback" AS "p" LEFT JOIN "Ads" AS "a" ON "p"."customer_id"="a"."customer_id") AS "A" GROUP BY "A"."session_id") AS "B" WHERE "B"."max_label"=0

SELECT "session_id" FROM "playback" WHERE "session_id" NOT IN (SELECT "session_id" FROM "playback" AS "p" LEFT JOIN "ads" AS "a" ON "p"."customer_id"="a"."customer_id" WHERE "p"."start_time"<="a"."timestamp" AND "a"."timestamp"<="p"."end_time")

SELECT DISTINCT "p2"."session_id" AS "session_id" FROM ("playback" AS "p1" JOIN "ads" AS "a" ON "a"."customer_id"="p1"."customer_id" AND "a"."timestamp"<="p1"."end_time" AND "a"."timestamp">="p1"."start_time") RIGHT JOIN "playback" AS "p2" ON "p2"."session_id"="p1"."session_id" WHERE "p1"."session_id" IS NULL
